    <li>Gesture controls</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Installation Instructions</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>Download the APK files from the links above</li>
    <li>Enable "Unknown Sources" in Settings > Security</li>
    <li>Open the downloaded APK file</li>
    <li>Tap "Install" when prompted</li>
    <li>Wait for installation to complete</li>
    <li>Open the app from your app drawer</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Requirements</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Android 4.3 or higher</li>
    <li>Unknown Sources enabled</li>
    <li>Approximately 50MB free space for all apps</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Note</h2>

  <p>
